snippet.title: Eiyuu Senki - The World Conquest - English Opening (PS3)
snippet.description:
English opening movie for Eiyuu Senki - The World Conquest.
Opening theme "Infinite Melody" performed by Imai Asami.
 
Prepare to battle cute world leaders in this Tactical RPG developed by TENCO, 5pb. and MAGES. and localized by Fruitbat Factory.

Now available on PlayStation 3(tm) in Europe, Australia and New Zealand!
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/eiyuu-senki-the-world-conquest-ps3/

North America: November 24.
https://store.sonyentertainmentnetwork.com/#!/cid=EP4951-NPEB02102_00-EIYUUSENKIDL0010

http://fruitbatfactory.com/eiyuusenki
